## Wiki Lifecycle Phases

| Phase | Skills | Purpose |
|-------|--------|---------|
| 1. Acquisition | ingest-source, batch-ingest, web-research | Bring new sources into the wiki |
| 2. Compilation | update-entities, update-concepts, cross-reference, update-overview, file-answer | Build wiki pages from sources and from answers worth keeping |
| 3. Analysis | query-wiki, generate-comparison, adversarial-review | Extract insights from the wiki |
| 4. Synthesis | compile-output, generate-slides, export-report, periodic-digest | Create deliverables and recurring summaries |
| Maintenance | lint-wiki, reindex, stats, resolve-contradiction, supersede-claim, deduplicate, decay-and-verify | Keep the wiki healthy, current, and consistent |
